### Example 4: Multi-line Continuous Summaries




::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
trial |>
  tbl_summary(
    by = trt,
    include = age,
    type = all_continuous() ~ "continuous2",
    statistic = all_continuous() ~ c(
      "{N_nonmiss}",
      "{median} ({p25}, {p75})",
      "{min}, {max}"
    ),
    missing = "no"
  ) |>
  add_p(pvalue_fun = label_style_pvalue(digits = 2))
```

